column2: SELECT id.allamID, id.ra1, id.dec1, id.ra2, id.dec2, id.allam_redshift1, id.allam_redshift2, id.objID as objID_dr7, id.run as run_dr7, id.camcol as camcol_dr7, id.field as field_dr7, id.obj as obj_dr7, id.ra as ra_dr7, id.dec as dec_dr7, id.specObjID as specObjID_dr7, p.objID, p.run, p.camcol, p.field, p.obj, p.ra, p.dec, p.specObjID into mydb.pmetric2 FROM mydb.MP2 as id JOIN dr1#.PhotoObjAll as p ON p.run = id.run WHERE p.camcol = id.camcol AND p.field = id.field AND p.obj = id.obj ORDER BY id.allamID
